Validation Rules
Product
product_code: required, unique, max 100 chars

product_type: must be valid enum value

For BULK: min_batch_size_kg <= batch_size_step_kg

shelf_life_days: positive integer or null

BillOfMaterial
parent_product_id != child_product_id (no self-reference)

quantity > 0

No circular dependencies (validate on insert)

Batch
batch_number: auto-generated, format "BATCH-YYYY-NNN"

product_id: must reference BULK product type

quantity_kg: must be >= product.min_batch_size_kg

status transitions: PLANNED → IN_PROGRESS → (COMPLETED | FAILED)

InventoryBalance
quantity >= 0

reserved_quantity >= 0

reserved_quantity <= quantity

expiry_date >= production_date (if both set)

ManufacturingOrder
If order_type = INTERNAL_BULK: parent_order_id must be set

If is_consolidated = True: source_order_ids must not be empty

priority: auto-calculated from due_date for SHIP orders

